1
00:00:00,499 --> 00:00:05,023
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

2
00:00:05,023 --> 00:00:10,527
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

3
00:00:10,527 --> 00:00:16,955
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

4
00:00:16,955 --> 00:00:21,435
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

5
00:00:21,435 --> 00:00:25,883
♪Holding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey♪

6
00:00:25,883 --> 00:00:30,794
♪The chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another♪

7
00:00:30,794 --> 00:00:34,843
♪The promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten♪

8
00:00:34,843 --> 00:00:39,378
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

9
00:00:39,378 --> 00:00:43,675
♪Start the countdown 4321,
a new scenery♪

10
00:00:43,675 --> 00:00:48,440
♪I want to see all the scenes about you♪

11
00:00:48,440 --> 00:00:51,931
♪No need to miss you anymore♪

12
00:00:51,931 --> 00:00:55,611
♪Right by your side♪

13
00:00:57,257 --> 00:01:00,635
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,635 --> 00:01:03,040
=Episode 19=

15
00:01:19,966 --> 00:01:21,664
Lan, you're bad.

16
00:01:22,112 --> 00:01:23,700
You keep me waiting.

17
00:01:25,533 --> 00:01:26,766
Why do you want to meet at home?

18
00:01:27,066 --> 00:01:28,333
It wastes time.

19
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:32,166
I'm not late. You're early.

20
00:01:32,233 --> 00:01:33,500
I came five minutes early.

21
00:01:35,066 --> 00:01:36,766
No big deal.

22
00:01:37,966 --> 00:01:39,333
I've been a frequent visitor
to your house.

23
00:01:39,566 --> 00:01:41,400
I like to discuss matters here.

24
00:01:42,733 --> 00:01:44,466
Just as usual, have some juice?

25
00:01:44,633 --> 00:01:46,033
Yes, with less ice.

26
00:01:56,733 --> 00:01:59,633
I never thought this day would come.

27
00:01:59,866 --> 00:02:01,633
You personally ask me for design.

28
00:02:04,266 --> 00:02:05,833
You can reject me.

29
00:02:07,666 --> 00:02:10,099
How could I?

30
00:02:10,266 --> 00:02:14,033
We've been friends since childhood.

31
00:02:25,266 --> 00:02:28,133
My company has some financial problems,

32
00:02:28,833 --> 00:02:31,800
but there are plenty of R&D teams
that want to work with me.

33
00:02:32,433 --> 00:02:34,033
If you're not interested,

34
00:02:34,133 --> 00:02:35,200
after finishing your juice,

35
00:02:35,266 --> 00:02:36,400
you can leave.

36
00:02:37,033 --> 00:02:38,166
This is non-alcoholic.

37
00:02:40,066 --> 00:02:41,899
You're still so charming.

38
00:02:42,066 --> 00:02:43,866
With such a low budget,

39
00:02:44,133 --> 00:02:45,200
you still keep confident.

40
00:02:49,533 --> 00:02:52,700
My family has
been eyeing cosmetic market.

41
00:02:53,133 --> 00:02:57,033
Aren't you afraid
I'll mess up your new product?

42
00:02:58,533 --> 00:03:00,333
As the top designer in the city,

43
00:03:00,866 --> 00:03:01,999
I don't think

44
00:03:02,033 --> 00:03:03,900
you'll sully your reputation.

45
00:03:05,133 --> 00:03:06,566
You know me so well.

46
00:03:08,966 --> 00:03:10,733
Your family may be well financed

47
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:12,900
but in a sunset industry.

48
00:03:13,433 --> 00:03:15,766
If you cooperate with me,

49
00:03:16,766 --> 00:03:17,733
for you,

50
00:03:17,966 --> 00:03:19,966
it can be a chance to test the market.

51
00:03:20,666 --> 00:03:21,833
How?

52
00:03:24,233 --> 00:03:27,300
I know your family also
wants a piece of the cosmetic market.

53
00:03:27,933 --> 00:03:29,533
That's why I want to work with you.

54
00:03:30,833 --> 00:03:32,233
You bear half of the R&D costs

55
00:03:32,433 --> 00:03:34,400
as a technology investment.

56
00:03:34,533 --> 00:03:36,033
I only pay the other half in cash.

57
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:39,766
After success,
I'll give you all the market research

58
00:03:39,866 --> 00:03:41,933
and share profits
with you proportionally.

59
00:03:43,533 --> 00:03:45,366
In this way, you can participate deeply

60
00:03:45,533 --> 00:03:47,100
and test the market.

61
00:03:48,233 --> 00:03:50,200
We can do it all by ourselves.

62
00:03:50,266 --> 00:03:51,600
Why cooperate with you?

63
00:03:54,033 --> 00:03:55,233
Around the entire country,

64
00:03:55,366 --> 00:03:56,999
which company

65
00:03:57,133 --> 00:03:59,233
has better brand recognition

66
00:03:59,766 --> 00:04:01,184
and bigger market share than We Group?

67
00:04:03,733 --> 00:04:06,100
It's a shortcut for you. Think about it.

68
00:04:06,433 --> 00:04:07,800
If you don't invest,

69
00:04:08,733 --> 00:04:09,733
I'll find someone else.

70
00:04:09,833 --> 00:04:10,400
You...

71
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,033
Stop.

72
00:04:11,533 --> 00:04:13,533
Your budge is extremely low,

73
00:04:13,833 --> 00:04:16,933
and half of it is on us.

74
00:04:17,866 --> 00:04:21,300
Only a bold person can say such a thing.

75
00:04:21,966 --> 00:04:22,899
Deal.

76
00:04:27,166 --> 00:04:27,966
Good.

77
00:04:28,733 --> 00:04:31,566
All the projects
of this quarter are outsourced to you.

78
00:04:33,433 --> 00:04:37,433
May I ask what are your ideas
for the new products of the new quarter?

79
00:04:39,533 --> 00:04:41,300
We should create a product,

80
00:04:41,866 --> 00:04:45,200
a multi-component product
that is rare on the market.

81
00:04:48,133 --> 00:04:54,500
It contains plant oils, waxes,
hydrocarbons, synthetic fats,

82
00:04:55,066 --> 00:04:56,133
fatty acids, esters and emulsifiers.

83
00:04:57,933 --> 00:05:01,100
The six basic ingredients
can make a new product.

84
00:05:01,933 --> 00:05:05,566
To give cosmetics a new function,

85
00:05:05,966 --> 00:05:08,566
it requires
important functional ingredients.

86
00:05:08,992 --> 00:05:12,300
It has effects like moisturizing,
sun protection, antioxidant

87
00:05:12,448 --> 00:05:13,533
- Excuse me.
- and whitening.

88
00:05:13,533 --> 00:05:14,333
Okay.

89
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:17,400
We'll talk about the details later.

90
00:05:18,533 --> 00:05:19,333
Not bad.

91
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:21,400
Take moisturization for example.

92
00:05:22,133 --> 00:05:24,433
It is important to ensure the stability
of the product's PH value.

93
00:05:26,266 --> 00:05:29,933
In that case, we can find...

94
00:05:32,333 --> 00:05:34,432
Miss Jin, where are you going?

95
00:05:35,333 --> 00:05:36,900
I'm going out for some air.

96
00:05:36,933 --> 00:05:38,366
Alright, this way please.

97
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:39,800
You can rest here for a while.

98
00:05:46,033 --> 00:05:47,333
Miss Jin.

99
00:05:50,933 --> 00:05:54,500
Chen and you are here
to discuss the R&D?

100
00:05:54,566 --> 00:05:55,400
Yes, Mrs. Lan.

101
00:05:56,900 --> 00:05:57,700
Have a seat.

102
00:06:08,500 --> 00:06:09,300
Miss Jin.

103
00:06:11,666 --> 00:06:13,033
This is a black card

104
00:06:13,833 --> 00:06:15,333
without spending limit.

105
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:22,600
Well,

106
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:25,536
you're not the kind of girl
who loves material comforts.

107
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,700
In this world...

108
00:06:27,733 --> 00:06:28,433
Mr. Lan and I...

109
00:06:28,466 --> 00:06:29,233
I know.

110
00:06:32,066 --> 00:06:32,900
I know

111
00:06:34,366 --> 00:06:36,399
Chen is longing

112
00:06:36,766 --> 00:06:38,400
for his true love.

113
00:06:40,333 --> 00:06:41,664
After spending time with you,

114
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:44,833
I can see that you're a good girl.

115
00:06:44,933 --> 00:06:46,900
But you should be clear

116
00:06:49,248 --> 00:06:53,088
Chen and Qianqian grew up together.

117
00:06:54,133 --> 00:06:55,488
They know each other pretty well.

118
00:06:58,766 --> 00:07:01,133
And our two families hope

119
00:07:01,166 --> 00:07:03,166
to become one.

120
00:07:08,666 --> 00:07:10,033
In that case,

121
00:07:11,866 --> 00:07:14,633
I have to be Lan Chen's girlfriend.

122
00:07:19,216 --> 00:07:22,240
(Lan Rensha is asking for a video call.)

123
00:07:23,366 --> 00:07:25,166
I won't disturb you.

124
00:07:27,466 --> 00:07:29,333
Are you Miss Jin?

125
00:07:31,133 --> 00:07:31,933
Yes.

126
00:07:32,466 --> 00:07:36,833
Ignorant. Do you know
you're ruining my grandson's future?

127
00:07:39,433 --> 00:07:43,366
Is that so? How?

128
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:47,104
What can you bring to my grandson?

129
00:07:47,833 --> 00:07:49,666
You're not from our social class.

130
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:52,200
Temporary heartthrob means nothing.

131
00:07:53,066 --> 00:07:56,200
Indeed, we're not
of the same social class.

132
00:07:56,433 --> 00:07:59,400
You guys inhumanely execute plans
in business wars,

133
00:07:59,566 --> 00:08:01,800
disregarding emotions.

134
00:08:02,333 --> 00:08:03,840
I'm from an ordinary family,

135
00:08:04,766 --> 00:08:06,333
but I have a joyous childhood.

136
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:10,133
I have friends and family
and bravely pursue what we like.

137
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:16,700
In that sense,
we do come from two different worlds.

138
00:08:17,200 --> 00:08:22,133
Nonsense, you think
you understand my grandson?

139
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:33,966
Then how much do you know
about your grandson or son?

140
00:08:38,366 --> 00:08:40,266
His favorite thing is fashion design.

141
00:08:40,266 --> 00:08:42,533
He got into
the best fashion design university,

142
00:08:43,066 --> 00:08:45,533
but for your family business,

143
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:48,100
he went to a cosmetic university.

144
00:08:49,033 --> 00:08:51,040
When he needed your affirmation,

145
00:08:52,533 --> 00:08:54,433
all you gave him was pressure.

146
00:08:56,566 --> 00:08:58,080
So he closed himself off

147
00:08:59,266 --> 00:09:00,966
and became unusually cautious.

148
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:03,136
Are you satisfied

149
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:05,366
with what he is now?

150
00:09:06,766 --> 00:09:08,299
Miss Jin.

151
00:09:11,033 --> 00:09:15,033
Don't be so self-righteous.
Believe it or not, I can ruin you.

152
00:09:17,066 --> 00:09:20,096
You rich people are condescending.

153
00:09:20,966 --> 00:09:23,333
Since Lan Chen took over the group,

154
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:24,864
he's been lonely every day.

155
00:09:25,366 --> 00:09:27,566
He has to face

156
00:09:27,566 --> 00:09:29,166
and solve many problems alone.

157
00:09:29,666 --> 00:09:32,800
Who among you truly cares for
and trusts him?

158
00:09:35,566 --> 00:09:37,166
You only rush him

159
00:09:37,166 --> 00:09:39,200
to get the investment
from Lihuai International.

160
00:09:40,733 --> 00:09:43,633
In my eyes, he's a strong man.

161
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:46,033
He never backs down or runs away.

162
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:49,300
He carries the weight of thousands
of employees on his shoulders.

163
00:09:49,833 --> 00:09:54,833
The Gu family is wealthy.
Gu Qianqian is Zeng Huaishi's cousin.

164
00:09:55,266 --> 00:09:56,066
Right?

165
00:09:57,933 --> 00:10:02,433
But Lan Chen refused the marriage alliance
and didn't take the shortcut.

166
00:10:02,566 --> 00:10:04,800
He relies on himself
to fulfill his mission.

167
00:10:06,333 --> 00:10:12,448
I only hope
after he completes his mission,

168
00:10:14,166 --> 00:10:16,233
you can let him do what he wants to do.

169
00:10:17,233 --> 00:10:20,233
Shut up. You're fired.
Get out of my company.

170
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:21,833
Who dares to fire my secretary?

171
00:10:24,576 --> 00:10:27,233
Impudent. How dare you
talk to me like that.

172
00:10:27,233 --> 00:10:28,000
Grandpa.

173
00:10:28,866 --> 00:10:30,240
Nobody can fire my secretary.

174
00:10:30,733 --> 00:10:31,680
Moreover,

175
00:10:32,433 --> 00:10:33,633
she's my woman.

176
00:10:36,466 --> 00:10:37,472
How dare you.

177
00:10:38,033 --> 00:10:39,100
I'm in charge of the company.

178
00:10:41,166 --> 00:10:44,733
Miss Jin, I'm done.

179
00:10:45,333 --> 00:10:46,666
Let's go eat.

180
00:10:46,733 --> 00:10:48,699
Alright, I'm a bit hungry.

181
00:10:48,733 --> 00:10:49,733
Chen.

182
00:10:49,733 --> 00:10:54,112
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

183
00:10:54,112 --> 00:10:58,574
♪Holding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey♪

184
00:10:58,574 --> 00:11:03,328
♪The chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another♪

185
00:11:03,328 --> 00:11:07,456
♪The promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten♪

186
00:11:07,456 --> 00:11:11,872
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

187
00:11:11,872 --> 00:11:16,439
♪Start the countdown 4321,
a new scenery♪

188
00:11:17,971 --> 00:11:22,493
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

189
00:11:25,523 --> 00:11:30,484
♪As if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other♪

190
00:11:33,533 --> 00:11:39,357
♪When the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in♪

191
00:11:39,357 --> 00:11:45,824
♪You come with light,
shining into my heart♪

192
00:11:46,528 --> 00:11:50,308
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

193
00:11:50,308 --> 00:11:54,429
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

194
00:11:54,429 --> 00:11:56,125
♪Open my secret♪

195
00:11:56,125 --> 00:12:02,173
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

196
00:12:02,173 --> 00:12:06,045
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

197
00:12:06,045 --> 00:12:10,551
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

198
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:19,261
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪
